page.title: 01My Road.
page.content: Bruntwood Avenue. In my road there are 52 houses but only 50 have garages. At No.7 there are four people living there. Two are children and the husband works at Hazel Grove. At No.9 there are 4 people. Two are children. The wife works at Augustus Barnett and the husband works in Sharston. At No.11 there are four people. They have lived there for about 3 years and the wife works at Wythenshawe Hospital. At No.14 there are 3 people who have lived there for 15 years. The husband works at the Airport. A No.23 there are 2 people. They have lived there for 20 years, and the husband works at the Airport. At No.42 there are 4 people who have lived there for over 9 years and the husband works in Manchester.
